OL,3,CEaster tourism 'better than expected'
OL,4,Cas businesses hope for spring boost
OL,6,FITV News' Sam Blackledge spoke to St
OL,7,FIves traders as the Easter holidays
OL,8,Fkick off
OL,10,FThe Easter holidays are well underway
OL,11,F- and despite the changeable weather,
OL,12,FWest Country tourism bosses say
OL,13,Ffootfall has been better than expected.
OL,15,FThe Visit Cornwall chairman explained
OL,16,Fthat the Easter break is vital to the
OL,17,Fregion's economy and that traders and
OL,18,Fholidaymakers are hoping the rain
OL,19,Fstays away this fortnight.
