OL,3,CEaster tourism 'better than expected'
OL,4,Cas businesses hope for spring boost
OL,6,FSimon Townsend, general manager of the
OL,7,FEden Project, said: "Easter has been
OL,8,Freally busy, a great start to the
OL,9,Fholidays.
OL,11,F"We're really happy with it. We had a
OL,12,Fgood year last year, up about 14 per
OL,13,Fcent on the year before. And so we can
OL,14,Fsee that slow trend coming out of
OL,15,FCovid for the last couple of years."
